    public class OpenTicketFragment
extends TicketFragment
implements ReverseGeocoder.ReverseGeocodingListener, com.google.android.gms.maps.GoogleMap.OnCameraMoveListener
    This is a concrete implementation of TicketFragment class to present Open tickets.
    This fragment will receive location change broadcast from LocationService in every 5 seconds and update it on the map. In onResume() of this fragment, interval of location listener has been updated with 5 seconds and service is restarted. By restarting the service, FusedLocationProvider will be initialised again with new interval.

    mohsin.khan
